The second wife was Joan Fisher, the second daughter of Ronald Fisher. He died on March 28, 2013 at the age of 93 [1]. Awards
1964 - Guy's Silver Medal[en]
1968 - Shewhart Medal
1972 - Wilkes Memorial Award[en]
1974 - R. A. Fisher Lectureship
1985 - Fellow of the Royal Society of London[en]*
1990 - Guggenheim Fellowship[2]
1993 - Guy's Gold Medal[en]
2003 - George Box Medal